# ── Proprietary-import denylist — gate G3 (spec 07 §8.4, SC-6) ───────────────
#
# One regex per line, applied line-by-line to every *.py file in the staged
# public tree by .github/scripts/mirror_gates.py on EVERY sync (tag push AND
# manual dispatch) before any push. Any match turns the sync red.
#
# The first two patterns are the sdk-release.yml proprietary-import check
# (`^from components |^import components `), moved from release-only to the
# publication boundary. `[ ]` encodes the significant trailing space so
# whitespace-stripping tooling cannot silently weaken the pattern. The third
# closes the bare-import variant the original grep missed. Extensible: add
# patterns here; the gate reads this file on every sync.
#
# Published beside the allowlist so the boundary is third-party-auditable.
^from components[ ]
^import components[ ]
^import components$
